<h3 id="summary">Summary</h3>

<p>In Matplotlib, class is following the rule <strong>Figure -&gt; Axes -&gt; (Line2D, Text, etc)</strong>.
One Figure can contain several Axes. Use Axes in Matplotlib indicates a plotting area.</p>

